  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: Beetroot juice increases the exercise tolerance of patients with chronic lung
      disease.

      Using the already established pulmonary rehabilitation model, we aim to split the group of 8
      into 2 groups, each group taking 500ml of beetroot juice 24 hours before there class on
      alternate (differing) weeks to see if it improves their overall exercise tolerance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
